u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>A Eracle.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":317,"html":318},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The dedication is written in an alphabet aberrant to the context of Syracuse, in which it was found. According to Jeffery (1961), the alphabet is of the Megarian type, which she explains by suggesting that those (the pacheis) transported by Gelon to Syracuse from Megara Hyblaea had made a dedication using, for reasons she does not further investigate, the alphabet of the mother country. According to Guarducci (1959-1960), on the other hand, the alphabet would undoubtedly be Corinthian and could easily be explained by the presence of Corinthians or Corcyraeans in Syracuse around the fifth century.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":320,"html":321},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Jeffery J.WC.MegH.30.p.01 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002294\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002294\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Guarducci 1959-1960 250, fig. 2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001928\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001928\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Jeffery 1961 276 no.30 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000677\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000677\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1989 75, fig. 13 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Dubois 1989 \u003Ca href=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\" target=\"_blank\">90\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Jeffery Johnston 1990 276 no.30 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000678\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000678\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1998 95 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000637\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000637\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":323,"html":324},"handnote","  \u003Cp> Types list: \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ι-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ι type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Κ-type1.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Κ type1.1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Λ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Λ type2\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1\u003C/a> \u003Ca href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ρ-type1.5.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ρ type1.5\u003C/a> \u003C/p> Line 1    ",{"id":326,"html":327},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[329,331,334,335],{"html":330},"Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa",{"id":332,"lang":153,"html":333},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\"